==English==

===Pronunciation===
;Homophones
*[[manner]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# A [[landed]] [[estate]].
# The main [[house]] of such an estate or a similar residence; a [[mansion]].
# A [[district]] over which a [[feudal]] [[lord]] could [[exercise]] certain [[right]]s and [[privilege]]s in [[medieval]] [[western]] [[Europe]].
# The lord's [[residence]] and seat of control in such a district.

